Murgitroyd Group plc



05/07/2017 | News release | Distributed by Public on 05/07/2017 18:40
Murgitroyd Sponsors Innovation Award at Elevator Awards 2017 – Congratulations DDK Positioning! 5 July 2017








[Attachment] The Elevator Awards 2017 took place last Thursday (29 June) and Murgitroyd was there as proud sponsor of The Grampian Award for Innovation.
      

        The annual award ceremony, which was held at the Mercure Ardoe House Hotel, celebrates business excellence, entrepreneurial behaviour and outstanding community contributions made by top businesses in Aberdeen City and Aberdeenshire.
      

        Murgitroyd's James Brown (Director, Patents) presented DDK Positioning with the Grampian Award for Innovation for its early-stage product which the judges said had 'the potential to be game-changing across a wide range of industries'.
      

[Attachment]DDK Positioning provides precise positioning solutions for consumer applications which can be delivered on handheld devices such as mobile phones.
      

        They beat off strong competition from RigDeluge who produce innovative solutions and products for onshore and offshore firefighting systems and Aiken Group who provide cost-effective environmental and waste water treatment solutions for both onshore and offshore industries.
      

        A video outlining all of the three finalists' solutions can be viewed here.
      

        You can find the full list of winners from the night by visiting Elevator UK's website - elevatoruk.com


RECENT NEWS

          Murgitroyd Sponsors Innovation Award at Elevator Awards 2017 - Congratulations DDK Positioning!
        














